<section class="hero">
  <div class="wrap hero-grid">
    <div>
      <h1 class="rise">Hi, I'm Francisca.</h1>
      <p class="lede rise d1">If this is your first time here, chances are we met at an event, you came across something I wrote, found me through LinkedIn, or simply stumbled onto this little corner of the internet. However you got here, I'm really glad you did.</p>
      <p class="lede rise d1">I have a biomedical engineering background that has taken a detour into health systems, health informatics, and health policy. I'm also pumped about organizations, the structures, operations, and processes that make or mar them.</p>
      <p class="lede rise d2">If any of that sounds interesting, I'd love for you to stay awhile. And if you'd simply like to have a conversation, my inbox is always open.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="rise d2">
      <div class="portrait-frame">
        <img
          class="portrait"
          src="{{ settings.portrait or '/images/portrait.svg' }}"
          alt="Portrait of {{ site.name }}"
          onerror="this.onerror=null;this.src='/images/portrait.svg';"
        />
      </div>
      <p class="portrait-name">{{ site.name }}</p>
      <p class="portrait-role">{{ site.role }}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="block" id="academic">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">Academic Engagement</p>
    <p class="block-lede">I spend a good part of my time reading, researching, and writing about health systems, health policy, and health informatics.</p>
    <p class="block-lede">Here you'll find my reflections, analyses, and ongoing exploration of the ideas shaping my academic journey.</p>
    <p class="cta-row"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/academic/">Read my work →</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="block" id="professional">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="eyebrow">Professional Practice</p>
    <p class="block-lede">I've always been fascinated by organizational leadership. I am interested in organizational management, operations, and process improvement because I believe that successful organizations rarely succeed by accident.</p>
    <p class="block-lede">I share what I am learning, have learned, experienced, and just my thoughts.</p>
    <p class="cta-row"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/professional/">Read my work →</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="block" id="newsletter">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="block-lede">I'd love to occasionally send you thoughtful updates whenever I have something worth sharing.</p>
    <form name="newsletter" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field" class="newsletter-form">
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="newsletter" />
      <p hidden><label>Don't fill this out: <input name="bot-field" /></label></p>
      <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email" aria-label="Email" required />
      <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Subscribe</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
